{"title":"祸心毕露","authors":["池北偶","朱根华"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":3,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"祸心毕露"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗  朱根华画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本防卫厅长官野吕田芳成近日说，日本可以先发制人地攻击企图用导弹袭击日本的国家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本妖风阵阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战犯借尸还魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后裔继承衣钵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总想旧梦重温。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大搞历史翻案，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不断设法扩军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"觉得羽毛丰满，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更是嚣张万分。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要走祖宗老路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬言先发制人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要找个借口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便可悍然寻衅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黩武祸心毕露，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端的头脑发昏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知天高地厚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄图扭转乾坤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若敢铤而走险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能玩火自焚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒是警醒人们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切莫掉以轻心。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}